    <tr><td>Complexity in billing systems</td><td>Medium</td><td>Build per-booking commission logic into Generate Commission from the start, even if not differentiated yet.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Venues gaming the system (switching booking types)</td><td>Low</td><td>Booking type is set by the booking flow, not venue preference. Monitor for anomalies.</td></tr>
  </table>

